
****************************
This program is written for Python3
Usage: python3 circbuff.py

Specify input file as: inputfile.txt or change in program
Output file is: outputfile.txt or change to anything else (WARNING: This file will be over written.)

You can also specify the directories where the files are read and written to as: IN_DIR and OUT_DIR
****************************

Program to read file in bytes, write the bytes to a buffer (in bytes), and write those bytes to a file

specify input and output file names in circbuff.py
Change size of buffer as N
The file should be less than the size of N or else the buffer will be overwritten.
Also, the program kicks out if the file size is greater than N.

author: Prasad Golla
